{"title":"Old Man Mountain Drops Prices on Fit Kits","link":"https://theradavist.com/old-man-mountain-drops-prices-on-fit-kits/","date":1739377988000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/08/220818_ErikHillard_ElkhornAxle-003.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/08/220818_ErikHillard_ElkhornAxle-003.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/08/220818_ErikHillard_ElkhornAxle-003.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2022/08/220818_ErikHillard_ElkhornAxle-003.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Not all financial news is bad. <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/old-man-mountain/\" target=\"_blank\">Old Man Mountain</a> just dropped the prices on its <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2Ffit-kits-and-spare-parts%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Fit Kits</a> by 15%.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-8.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-8.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-13.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-13.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/Old-Man-Mountain-Basket-Review-13.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>But how did this happen? This past fall, Old Man Mountain invested in a new CNC machine. This was done in order to keep up with demand and improve their manufacturing efficiency. This new efficiency reduced the cost to make their axles by a fair amount. Rather than pocket this newly found profit and take a long vacation in 2025 they are passing the savings on to their customers.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-12.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-12.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-12.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-11.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-11.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/08/2023-MADE-Bike-Show-Old-Man-Mountain-Digit-Datum-Full-Suspension-11.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Prices are dropping 15% from $80 to $68!</p>\n<p>Supporting companies like this is more important now than ever. So check out the savings at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9810ede6-4922-46d9-b096-e2993c490cc6&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Foldmanmountain.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\">Old Man Mountain</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/old-man-mountain-drops-prices-on-fit-kits/\">Old Man Mountain Drops Prices on Fit Kits</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"98a843da40889ec3adc21d3af1ddcda2c423adb54d0d2eaf409c020a72e27e71","category":"Cycling"}